═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
4. FORKS AND DERIVATIVE WORKS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

If you create a fork or derivative work:

REQUIRED:
✅ Choose a DIFFERENT name for your fork
✅ Include "Based on apiars" in your README
✅ Preserve copyright notices and license
✅ Clearly indicate your fork is NOT the official apiars project

EXAMPLES OF ACCEPTABLE FORK NAMES:
✅ "YourName API Fuzzer (based on apiars)"
✅ "OpenFuzz (apiars fork)"
✅ "CustomTool (derived from apiars)"

PROHIBITED:
❌ "apiars Community Edition"
❌ "apiars-plus"
❌ "Better-apiars"

