═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
6. TRADEMARK ENFORCEMENT
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

We will enforce trademark rights to:
- Prevent consumer confusion
- Protect the reputation of the apiars project
- Ensure quality control of products bearing the apiars name
- Prevent dilution of the trademark

PROCESS:
1. Informal notice (email requesting compliance)
2. Formal cease-and-desist letter (if no response)
3. Legal action (if necessary)

We prefer COOPERATION over litigation. If you receive a notice,
please respond promptly. Most trademark issues can be resolved
through simple name changes or clarifications.

